{"tid":2317156,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[人體/生物力學]想問一d肌肉既野","createTime":"2020-12-08T11:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:03:14.000Z","uid":70760,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"68e9ef37a5ddc9410f238c4338ef7729ee954fcf","tid":2317156,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"1. 肌肉有遠近固定&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;如果我用近固定發力方或練&nbsp;,&nbsp;咁佢遠固定時發力方式會唔會都會加強&nbsp;?<br />\n<br />\n例子&nbsp;:&nbsp;臀大肌&nbsp;近固定&nbsp;後伸&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;遠固定&nbsp;骨盤後傾<br />\n<br />\n例子&nbsp;:&nbsp;提肩胛肌   近固定，使肩胛骨上提&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;,&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;遠固定，一側收縮使頭頸向同側側屈、後伸；兩側收縮，使頭伸直<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.&nbsp;&nbsp;上網有4大不宜強化肌肉<br />\n<br />\n一、不可主動強化的4塊肌肉<br />\n1.肩胛提肌<br />\n<br />\n肌肉肥大會縮短肌肉和神經線的距離會壓迫神經線<br />\n2.胸小肌<br />\n<br />\n變大會導致肩關節能力減小關節壓力變大<br />\n3.斜角肌<br />\n<br />\n強化後肋骨上提，鎖骨和肋骨的空間變小，有機會壓迫神經線<br />\n4.髂腰肌<br />\n<br />\n強化會導致腰椎往前增加，骨盆前傾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇咩意見俾上交叉綜合症同骨盤前傾既人&nbsp;?&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;搵到髂腰肌應該要強化&nbsp;&nbsp;對嗎&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肩胛提肌&nbsp;&nbsp;斜角肌&nbsp;同&nbsp;胸小肌呢&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010e6c3287d3f1fa952d2f6fa0e5207b575d3380","tid":2317156,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:03:14.000Z","msg":"問得嚟都做撚完啦問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}